OL,3,CFuneral director appears in court on
OL,4,C63 charges
OL,6,FA funeral director has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with 63 offences
OL,8,Ffollowing an investigation into the
OL,9,Ftreatment of bodies at his premises.
OL,11,FRobert Bush, formerly of Kirk Ella,
OL,12,FEast Yorkshire, appeared briefly at
OL,13,FHull Magistrates' Court on Wednesday
OL,14,Fafter the year-long investigation into
OL,15,FLegacy Independent Funeral Directors.
