OL,3,CFuneral director appears in court on
OL,4,C63 charges
OL,6,FHe is charged with 30 counts of
OL,7,Fpreventing a lawful and decent burial
OL,8,Fand 30 counts of fraud by false
OL,9,Frepresentation relating to bodies
OL,10,Ffound at the firm's Hessle Road site
OL,11,Fin Hull in March last year.
OL,13,FThe 47-year-old has also been charged
OL,14,Fwith one count of fraudulent trading
OL,15,Fin relation to funeral plans sold
OL,16,Fbetween May 2012 and March 2024,
OL,17,Fencompassing 172 victims, and one
OL,18,Fcount of fraud in relation to human
OL,19,Fashes, encompassing 50 victims,
OL,20,Fbetween August 2017 and March 2024.
