OL,3,CFuneral director appears in court on
OL,4,C63 charges
OL,6,FBush, now of East Busk Lane, Otley,
OL,7,FWest Yorkshire, is also facing one
OL,8,Fcount of theft from charities between
OL,9,F1 September 2017 and 6 March 2024.
OL,11,FThe charities named in the charge
OL,12,Finclude Dove House Hospice and Working
OL,13,FIndependently Supporting Hull
OL,14,FHospitals (WISHH), The Salvation Army,
OL,15,FMacmillan Cancer Support, and Cystics
OL,16,Fof Hull Independent Equipment Fund
OL,17,F(CHIEF) which raises money for
OL,18,Ffamilies with cystic fibrosis patients.
