OL,3,CFuneral director appears in court on
OL,4,C63 charges
OL,6,FHe did not enter a plea during
OL,7,FWednesday's hearing and was given bail
OL,8,Fto appear at Hull Crown Court on
OL,9,FWednesday 13 August.
OL,11,FHumberside Police said they removed 35
OL,12,Fbodies and a quantity of ashes from
OL,13,FLegacy after receiving a report of
OL,14,Fconcern for care for the deceased in
OL,15,FMarch last year.
